<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>현재<sp/>Dali<sp/>UI<sp/>Text<sp/>Rendering<sp/>Pipeline<sp/>분석</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>목적</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이<sp/>문서의<sp/>목적은<sp/>현재<sp/>Dali<sp/>UI의<sp/>텍스트<sp/>렌더링<sp/>파이프라인을<sp/>`Label`,<sp/>`InputField`,<sp/>`text-controller`,<sp/>`text-view`,<sp/>`model`,<sp/>`layout`,<sp/>`text-atlas-renderer`,<sp/>`typesetter`<sp/>기준으로<sp/>정리하는<sp/>것이다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이번<sp/>문서에서는<sp/>다음<sp/>항목을<sp/>명확히<sp/>구분한다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`TextVisualizer`<sp/>구현에<sp/>직접<sp/>필요한<sp/>내용</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>구조<sp/>이해를<sp/>위한<sp/>참고용<sp/>내용</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">또한<sp/>분석<sp/>단계<sp/>규칙에<sp/>따라,<sp/>코드에서<sp/>확인한<sp/>사실만<sp/>기록하고<sp/>애매한<sp/>내용은<sp/>`확인<sp/>필요`로<sp/>표시한다.</highlight></codeline>
