<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>TextVisualizer<sp/>관점<sp/>해석</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>직접<sp/>필요한<sp/>내용</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">이번<sp/>범위에서<sp/>`TextVisualizer`가<sp/>style,<sp/>ellipsis,<sp/>underline,<sp/>shadow를<sp/>무시한다면,<sp/>atlas<sp/>renderer가<sp/>실제<sp/>plain<sp/>glyph<sp/>렌더링에<sp/>꼭<sp/>필요한<sp/>핵심<sp/>데이터는<sp/>아래로<sp/>좁아진다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>glyph<sp/>목록</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>glyph<sp/>position</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>기본<sp/>text<sp/>color</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>필요<sp/>시<sp/>glyph별<sp/>color<sp/>index</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>참고용<sp/>내용</highlight></codeline>
