<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>확인<sp/>필요<sp/>사항</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`AtlasRenderer`를<sp/>`TextVisualizer`용으로<sp/>더<sp/>축소한<sp/>별도<sp/>renderer<sp/>adapter<sp/>없이<sp/>바로<sp/>사용할지</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>아니면<sp/>`Text::ViewInterface`<sp/>최소<sp/>subset<sp/>구현으로<sp/>충분한지</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
