<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>참고<sp/>파일:<sp/>`public-api/input-field.h`,<sp/>`integration-api/input-field-impl.cpp`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`Text::Controller`가<sp/>담당하는<sp/>prepare<sp/>전<sp/>단계</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>script</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>font<sp/>fallback</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>shaping</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>glyph<sp/>metrics</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>line<sp/>break<sp/>candidate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`Text::Model`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>glyph와<sp/>glyph<sp/>position<sp/>전후<sp/>데이터를<sp/>보관하는<sp/>역할</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`Layout::Engine`</highlight></codeline>
